game.name: Barbie Fashion Mommy Dress
game.description:
Girls do not want to compromise on her look no matter whatever the occasion she has to get ready. Even almost every girl wants to look fabulous when she is pregnant. Today we have met with a cute princess Barbie who has a baby inside her tummy and is now seeking a new impressive look. Do you want to help her out in such a crucial time? Join Barbie Fashion Mommy Dress game and be prepared to guide her pick up some comfortable and beautiful clothes!

The best part is that her wardrobe does not have a shortage for the stylish and trendy pregnant outfits. Browse her wider outfit range to make her look as a fashionable pregnant woman in this brand new dressing game for girls! Do not choose the bad combination of dresses otherwise she has to face the criticism from her friends. Put your fashion taste and style sense to challenge to create a perfect dress for the doll in this html5 doll dress up game!

Give her doll a loose and long piece of dress and combine her outfits with a pair of nice matching shoes and other accessories! Choose a long cocktail outfit and low pumps for Barbie or give your favorite princess a flowy loose top and match it with a pair of simple and cute trousers! Keep mixing and matching all the outfit and accessory options until she is satisfied with your efforts! All the best to show your fashion knowledge and creativeness in our more popular Barbie games for kids!
